What are the advantages of using Hibernate over JDBC?

Answer- 

1.Hibernate stores java object to database directly.
2.supports pojo and poji.
3.Lighweight software because no need to install any kind of jar file
4.ORM persistence logic is database s/w independent
5.Prevents developer from writing boiler plate code
6.provides caching mechanism.
7.generated sql queries internally thats why efficient than jdbc.
8.exception handling is easy as compared to jdbc because throw unchecked exception
9.and has a special query language - JPQL java persistence query language

this are the advantages of using hibernate over jdbc.
